The installation is supported by providing an Eclipse update site in the depot. The realization of this is through http access to a set of file. For further information see: www.eclipse.org

Standard interfaces to Maven Repository and the Subversion Repository are used, and these are not documented further here.
To perform updates, users need an account at the Developer Depot with developer access to a project
Ontology repository is currently not in place, but is being considered both in context of Coding Assistant Tool and Service & Ontology modelling tools
